name: Water-and-Wastewater-Sensors-Data-Visualization
description: This R app explores water and wastewater sensor data via dynamic graphs. Users customize visuals, adjust the Y-axis, and use a summary table for key stats. A valuable tool for researchers and professionals, contributing to data-driven insights and enhancing decision-making in water and wastewater networks.

name: react-chart-editor
description: Customizable React-based editor panel for Plotly.js charts
